@startuml srs-change-sequence
!theme plain
title Sequence: SRS Change Detected

actor "Document Repository /\nVersion Control" as DocRepo
participant "Event\nReceiver" as Hook
participant "Parser" as Parser
participant "Classifier" as Class
participant "Resolver" as Res
participant "Document\nOwner" as Owner
participant "Workflow /\nTask System" as TaskSystem

DocRepo -> Hook: Document change event
Hook -> Parser: parse SRS diff
Parser -> Class: classify change\ntype (Risk/UI/etc)
Class -> Res: resolve impacted docs
Res -> Owner: send findings
Owner -> TaskSystem: acknowledge
note over Owner, TaskSystem: Owner reviews\nusing traceability tables
@enduml